metadata.name: Subtle emotions
metadata.description:
Subtle emotions begin to branch out solemn and intrusive...
The resonance of a distant memory is amplified
And inside there is still something that agitates me..
I see it, I feel it, I recognize myself, it's still me trying to understand those dreaded weaknesses and a complex fusion of emotions not yet fully explored

Self - portrait 
Made with double exposure techniques
